          <h2 class="post-title" itemprop="name headline">专访 YYKit 作者 ibireme: 开源大牛是怎样炼成的</h2>
        

        <div class="post-meta">
          <span class="post-time">
            
              <span class="post-meta-item-icon">
                <i class="fa fa-calendar-o"></i>
